{"id": "1184006436779474944", "channel_id": "1184006436779474944", "type": 0, "author_id": "472324940595593218", "author_name": "masaakiray", "author_bot": false, "content": "想詢問一下，以後是否會更新角色語音？\n在看劇情時角色都沒語音，感覺好奇怪@@\n還是說其實是我有設定沒用到，所以劇情裡角色才沒語音？", "timestamp": "2023-12-12T05:38:52.304000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1184006436779474944", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」角色語音", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1184283295337422910", "channel_id": "1184283295337422910", "type": 0, "author_id": "707847570424332338", "author_name": "yanhsi", "author_bot": false, "content": "（繁体中文中）萝坦的体重单位为ton而其余唤醒体单位均为lbs（除希洛外，不过她的单位是mina，而25mina仍然是常识范畴）。按照剧情并不能认为萝坦的体重达到该值。或许是我有没能够理解的部分知识，还望开发者解惑，谢谢！", "timestamp": "2023-12-12T23:59:00.528000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1184283295706525767", "filename": "f533334c8660d7f6a472e58c8725a03f.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 144180, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1184283295337422910/1184283295706525767/f533334c8660d7f6a472e58c8725a03f.png?ex=6a007304&is=69ff2184&hm=dd2436238cd366a5305cce716f7746f1cf23d213232d508c7b7ae20f079f3c3e&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1184283295337422910", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」角色档案中体重异常", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
