{"id": "1184146389513539704", "channel_id": "1184146389513539704", "type": 0, "author_id": "653590360802590730", "author_name": "divescott", "author_bot": false, "content": "在游戏中，无法通过点击卡面看到对应的衍生卡。\n\n比如艾瑞卡的0费卡机动武装-放和敛\n\n我想要看敛的效果实际上怎么都看不到，只有在对局中出牌的时候才能看。\n\n相同的问题也在造物上出现，某些造物会给卡组洗入灵感或者诅咒卡。比如造物［黑烛］，会洗入「蹒跚」，但是我看不到这个蹒跚是什么效果，无法进行抉择，只能凭游戏经验或者玩家总结的excel表来查。这是不合理的。\n\n我想要能够在点击卡面对应词条的时候能看到有什么样的效果。\n\n\n另一个问题在于多段伤害在对局怪物有受伤减力量之类的debuff时，动画时长过长的问题。\n\n比如对面怪物受伤减5点力量，我用艾瑞卡机动爆发打了6费的多段伤害时，对面怪物身上跳buff的时间过长。\n\n同样的问题在我方叠buff的时候也存在。对面多段伤害打在我身上，然后我身上跳了一串buff，然后跳buff的这个时长太长了，我只能干等，建议减短时间。特别是我身上有欲海浮沉类的受伤叠力量的命轮时，buff一直跳，挺耽误时间的，本来对局时间就比较长了", "timestamp": "2023-12-12T14:54:59.636000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1184146389513539704", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」衍生卡以及buff动画显示问题", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1184109697956069446", "channel_id": "1184109697956069446", "type": 0, "author_id": "1172138340275994645", "author_name": "cpeax_34497", "author_bot": false, "content": "可是活动栏那个红点非常——显眼诶…搞得我好难受的说，可以说说为什么不让他进物资了吗？", "timestamp": "2023-12-12T12:29:11.687000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1184109697956069446", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」坏，活动给的源质乐园不进入物资", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1184130043648167986", "channel_id": "1184130043648167986", "type": 0, "author_id": "1117794331336658994", "author_name": "icedexz", "author_bot": false, "content": "在超维额外回合被反击打至空血后死亡，使用应急灵知体后血条显示全满但血量仍然为0，结束回合后直接再次死亡，触发第二次应急灵知体提示，不太清楚是反击致死导致的还是超维回合死亡导致的，呜呜呜半个小时白打了🥹🥹🥹", "timestamp": "2023-12-12T13:50:02.478000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1184130044394733631", "filename": "Screenshot_20231212-213716.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 718455, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1184130043648167986/1184130044394733631/Screenshot_20231212-213716.png?ex=6a008d0a&is=69ff3b8a&hm=210901f3f0f2db604a2bc331b0e3e5656b551e95fb2a1e5c213a5422d3d3c997&"}, {"id": "1184130044910645340", "filename": "Screenshot_20231212-213730.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1140881, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1184130043648167986/1184130044910645340/Screenshot_20231212-213730.png?ex=6a008d0a&is=69ff3b8a&hm=ef9fc23ae8eef5e65e012347d16a64d102375be37b73b25c29fa0911933d05ed&"}, {"id": "1184130045543993415", "filename": "Screenshot_20231212-213738.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1642945, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1184130043648167986/1184130045543993415/Screenshot_20231212-213738.png?ex=6a008d0a&is=69ff3b8a&hm=0b96a6479309c59ca99c91140587e1a75a34935f3de74d2e47ddc198b34b817b&"}, {"id": "1184130046093426688", "filename": "Screenshot_20231212-213742.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 885906, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1184130043648167986/1184130046093426688/Screenshot_20231212-213742.png?ex=6a008d0b&is=69ff3b8b&hm=52f9e88f48917220fcd7d8f01ed79c87813c08e569f964da6332298b96647d00&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1184130043648167986", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」5-4 boss战 应急灵知体复活Bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181